<p><strong>Skills</strong> Arcana +5, History +5</p>

<p><strong>Languages</strong> Common, Draconic, Dwarvish, Elvish</p>

<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 0 (10 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>Spellcasting.</em></strong> Naxene is a 6th level spellcaster. Her spellcasting ability is Intelligence (spell save DC 13; +5 to hit with spell attacks). She has the following wizard spells prepared:</p>

<p>Cantrips (at will): fire bolt, light, mage hand, prestidigitation</p>

<p>1st level (4 slots): mage armor, magic missile, shield</p>

<p>2nd level (3 slots): misty step, suggestion</p>

<p>3rd level (3 slots): fly, lightning bolt</p>

<p><strong><em>Roleplaying Information.</em></strong> Goldenfields’ crops are vital Waterdeep’s survival, which is why the Watchful Order of Magists and Protectors sent Naxene to make sure the temple-farm is adeuately defended. At first she regarded the task as a punishment, but now she appreciates the peace and quiet.</p>

<p>Ideal: “There’s no problem that can’t be solved with magic.”</p>

<p>Bond: “I have great respect for Lady Laeral Silverhand of Waterdeep. She and the Lords’ Alliance are going to bring some much-needed order to this lawless land.”</p>

<p>Flaw: “I’m too smart to be wrong about anything.”</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Staff.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +1 to hit, reach 5 ft., one creature. Hit: 2 (1d6-1) bludgeoning damage, or 3 (1d8-1) bludgeoning damage if used with two hands.</p>

